Quest:Adepts of the Magi

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
House of the Magi

Given By: Old Cob

Giver Location: The Hive
This is a storyline quest.

Goals:
Go to the Adepts Chamber
Defeat the Spider Adepts
Talk to Old Cob
Hand In: Old Cob

Reward:

525
54,240
King Artorius (Balance)
King Artorius (Death)
King Artorius (Fire)
King Artorius (Ice)
King Artorius (Life)
King Artorius (Myth)
King Artorius (Storm)

Leads to:

Reflection of Shadow

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to Adepts of the Magi should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.
